{
  "texts": [
    "Secondly, the findings are constrained by the authors' available resources.",
    "Thirdly, the review exclusively focuses on English academic articles related to Metaverse technology in education, possibly excluding valuable contributions from non-English scholarship.",
    "Lastly, due to the nascent stage of Metaverse technology and limited research in databases like Web of Science and Scopus, a comprehensive overview of the field remains challenging.",
    "V. CONCLUSIONThe Metaverse demonstrates significant potential for transforming language education by providing innovative, immersive, and engaging learning experiences.",
    "The future of research in Metaverse-based English learning holds great promise."
  ]
}